Job Requirements:
Education:
- Bachelor degree and above

Experience:
1. Degree in law or Master of law;
2. At least 5 years in a legal manager/supervisor position in an international company (bank, fintech, insurance and financial institutions) is a must.
3. Can communicate in English

Knowledge and Skills:
- Critical and logical thinking;
- Proven ability to proactively provide insightful and timely legal support to stakeholders across a functionally;
